  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the world of classic puzzles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. It's easy for anyone to learn</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Push the block and use ice, conveyor belt, and walls to reach BLOCK+HOLE.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fall into the charm of class puzzle games with simple rules and in-depth gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rule 1. Number blocks and pushing</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3612000/extras/8f9bdd095fb28c7c09a2028e3fa66566.poster.avif?t=1753065762\" width=800 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3612000/extras/8f9bdd095fb28c7c09a2028e3fa66566.webm?t=1753065762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3612000/extras/8f9bdd095fb28c7c09a2028e3fa66566.mp4?t=1753065762\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the basic block, moves one space at a time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each time you move, the number of moves displayed on the block decreases by one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A block whose number of moves becomes 0 cannot be moved.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put number blocks into all holes prepared to clear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rule 2. Ice Block</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3612000/extras/05eab9dceeebff117308b2af2f5289cd.poster.avif?t=1753065762\" width=800 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3612000/extras/05eab9dceeebff117308b2af2f5289cd.webm?t=1753065762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3612000/extras/05eab9dceeebff117308b2af2f5289cd.mp4?t=1753065762\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ice blocks take one movement to slide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The slipped block moves until it meets a basic block or wall block.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rule 3. Conveyor Belt</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3612000/extras/6b067eb2b14c4cb72755d3bbbbe548fb.poster.avif?t=1753065762\" width=800 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3612000/extras/6b067eb2b14c4cb72755d3bbbbe548fb.webm?t=1753065762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3612000/extras/6b067eb2b14c4cb72755d3bbbbe548fb.mp4?t=1753065762\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The conveyor belt moves the number block in the direction indicated by the arrow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The number of moves is not counted while you are on the conveyor belt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rule 4. Wall blocks and number blocks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3612000/extras/4a50e6d6f7222bc9b31259b001203992.poster.avif?t=1753065762\" width=800 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3612000/extras/4a50e6d6f7222bc9b31259b001203992.webm?t=1753065762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3612000/extras/4a50e6d6f7222bc9b31259b001203992.mp4?t=1753065762\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is impossible to move where wall blocks and number blocks are.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you build a wall using number blocks, you can create a new movement path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. level maker</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you've enjoyed all the stages you've prepared, create your own level,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Share it with other users.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An infinite world of puzzles awaits you.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the world of classic puzzles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. It's easy for anyone to learn</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Push the block and use ice, conveyor belt, and walls to reach BLOCK+HOLE.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fall into the charm of class puzzle games with simple rules and in-depth gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rule 1. Number blocks and pushing</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3612000/extras/8f9bdd095fb28c7c09a2028e3fa66566.poster.avif?t=1753065762\" width=800 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3612000/extras/8f9bdd095fb28c7c09a2028e3fa66566.webm?t=1753065762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3612000/extras/8f9bdd095fb28c7c09a2028e3fa66566.mp4?t=1753065762\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the basic block, moves one space at a time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each time you move, the number of moves displayed on the block decreases by one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A block whose number of moves becomes 0 cannot be moved.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put number blocks into all holes prepared to clear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rule 2. Ice Block</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3612000/extras/05eab9dceeebff117308b2af2f5289cd.poster.avif?t=1753065762\" width=800 height=408 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.stea