ore_item_assets/steam/apps/3612000/extras/4a50e6d6f7222bc9b31259b001203992.webm?t=1753065762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3612000/extras/4a50e6d6f7222bc9b31259b001203992.mp4?t=1753065762\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is impossible to move where wall blocks and number blocks are.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you build a wall using number blocks, you can create a new movement path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. level maker</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you've enjoyed all the stages you've prepared, create your own level,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Share it with other users.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An infinite world of puzzles awaits you.</p>",
